        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "That’s where truth comes from.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Not the ‘truth’ of ‘he said, she said.’ Not the truth or moral righteousness or personal convictions. And certainly not the ‘truth’ of your political ideology or religion.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "But the truth of right here, right now—this is the world as it is.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Suffice to say, the longer you can sit in the interrogation room, the clearer your perceptions might be.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s not easy (interrogations rarely are), but it sure is worth it.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}